Package: RD1
Title: DBI Client and API Wrapper for Cloudflare D1
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Noam", "Ross", , "noam.ross+rd1@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A DBI-compliant database interface and API client for
    Cloudflare D1's serverless SQLite database. Provides wrappers for D1
    REST API endpoints, including time travel and bookmark-based
    restoration, plus convenience functions for common multi-step
    workflows such as exporting and downloading databases.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Depends:
    R (>= 4.1.0)
